    <briefdescription>
<para>Decorator that modifies values using increment/decrement keys. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This class wraps any element and adds behavior for increment and decrement keys. It calls the underlying element&apos;s Increment() method with +/- 1.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>T</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Base element type (must have Increment(signed char) method) </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kDec</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Key code for decrement </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>kInc</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Key code for increment </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
